commit.message:
fix sqla user manager example.

Fixes #647
doc fixed to add 'jsonb' as serialization format for AnyDict
a more permissive media type pattern
add MimeType and MediaType string specializations
parse gzip'd http request for spyne.twisted.http
update sql_crud example with a jsonb type
move sql examples to own dir

p_ctx.out_object itself can also be a Deferred.

memberize _cb_* and _eb_* functions
no need to convert mmap'd files to bytes objects

move FileData to spyne.model.relational

also make its "hidden" fields (those that don't get written
to the database) explicit

fix its serialization to bytes

Merge pull request #646 from cool-RR/patch-1

Use chain.from_iterable in msgpack.py
